service: dollar-quote-service

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.11
  region: us-east-2

functions:
  searchQuote: 
    handler: app.quote_handler.lambda_handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: quote
          method: get


plugins:
  - serverless-python-requirements
  - serverless-offline

custom:
  pythonRequirements:
    dockerizePIp: true
  dotenv:
    include:
      - QUOTE_API_URL_DOLLAR
      - PHONE_ID
      - TOKEN
      - PHONE_NUMBER_DESTINATION
